{"tid":1512740,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"事到如今，不如新增官員問責下台，為六大訴求","createTime":"2019-08-28T04:14:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T04:57:11.000Z","uid":5499,"like":4,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"afc05c95d1474d4635e991871781c16ca915c698","tid":1512740,"uid":5499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T04:14:15.000Z","msg":"講真，柒婆企到咁撚硬，唔踢走佢我地根本無辦法<br />\n<br />\n而家佢民望得番20%，應該係一個好時機<br />\n<br />\n唔好再話咩跛腳政府，而家佢咁低民望，正正係為所欲為，大肆鎮壓既理由，佢已經無野輸，打死罷就，佢而家先係真正玉石俱焚<br />\n<br />\n問責下台，以林鄭，鄭若驊，李家超三人為首，必須問責下台<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家討論下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6728ed8ee2c45f52437f9c6a996338dd7c0672b1","tid":1512740,"uid":284522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T04:14:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PWzcvgg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPWzcvgg.jpg&h=187c67d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=zAhFImnUcMh%2FonyB55KWQwqYqcROYCvJBJmaWwU8HGA%3D&h=fba8fcb4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=zAhFImnUcMh%2FonyB55KWQwqYqcROYCvJBJmaWwU8HGA%3D&h=92a8a918\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=zAhFImnUcMh%2FonyB55KWQwqYqcROYCvJBJmaWwU8HGA%3D&h=65a844dd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a>"},{"pid":"2b495b37dbd1e00f360ae7e572a256ad1539027f","tid":1512740,"uid":89145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T04:15:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"713658b449fca9